data.description:
Discover this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence spanning 2,488 square feet of living space.
Located in a convenient and sought-after area with parks and churches close by. This property boasts a host of desirable features: 
Spacious family room with a charming fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings,
An updated eat-in kitchen with a separate dining room. The master suite includes double sinks and a relaxing garden tub.
Upgraded hot water heater for energy efficiency and peace of mind.
Fresh interior paint throughout and brand new carpeting in the bedrooms ensures comfort and style.
Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this home your own. Contact us to schedule a viewing today!
